# generate palette
ffmpeg -i demo.mp4 -vf "fps=15,scale=640:-1:flags=lanczos,palettegen" -y palette.png
# create gif using palette
ffmpeg -i demo.mp4 -i palette.png -lavfi "fps=15,scale=640:-1:flags=lanczos [x]; [x][1:v] paletteuse" -y demo.gif

Notes:
- Use scale=640 or another width you prefer.
- On macOS, use QuickTime to record; on any OS, OBS works well.

